# 2p_anim_check — host. Diagnostic shot for the wan-fixes-3 remote-
# mech rendering: walk back and forth on Slipstream (no parallax
# overlay, so the body is fully visible on the client's view).
# Pairs with 2p_anim_check.client.shot.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/anim_host
network host 24171
name HostA
map slipstream

spawn_at 2300 1112
peer_spawn 1 2500 1112
aim 2500 1080

at 130 press right
at 220 release right
at 240 press left
at 360 release left
at 380 press right
at 470 release right

at 150 shot t150_start_right
at 200 shot t200_running_right
at 300 shot t300_running_left
at 420 shot t420_running_right
at 550 shot t550_stopped
at 650 end
